  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Associate Chiropractor",
  "description": "<p>Established in the neighbourhood of Serangoon in 2018, Reform Chiropractic is looking for a passionate and motivated chiropractor to join us in the coming year and beyond. Our main treatment method is diversified, activator and simple soft tissue releasing and exercise advice.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are ideally looking for someone with experience and strong manual adjusting skills however fresh graduates feel free to apply as skills can be grown, what is more important to us right now is that we find a personality that will mesh well with our team and with our patient base.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The ability to converse in mandarin would also be a plus as we are in a neighbourhood area, however we have staff that can translate so it is not imperative.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will be rewarded with attractive working hours and a base salary + commission system.</p>",
